{"tid":1479103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動議：新口號，「我要真普選」","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T08:24:24.000Z","uid":304551,"like":24,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"edac5d5377a8e575ab5e0e3d3c64078cd7da3ca6","tid":1479103,"uid":304551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:25:36.000Z","msg":"無普選，係一切問題既根源<br />\n亦係一代又一代抗爭者一直努力爭取<br />\n<br />\n今次係方法改變左<br />\n咁不如我地試下用新既方式叫「我要真普選」？<br />\n<br />\n係催淚煙中呼吸困難，說：「我要真普選」<br />\n<br />\n被失控黑警拘捕、毆打、布袋彈擊中，血流披面，說：「我要真普選」<br />\n<br />\n被白衣人追打至皮開肉爛，誓死反抗，說：「我要真普選」<br />\n<br />\n係街頭、地鐵、機場既所有不合作運動，跟市民道歉同時，說：「我要真普選」"},{"pid":"d046d0893ff1a3f1f98307cbf3d4cedeea0ba09c","tid":1479103,"uid":304551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5364da2b228ae78ead69b1ce12ba36c46aaaa282","tid":1479103,"uid":88263,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"動議<br />\n<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒中共 功德無量</span></span><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n林鄭、港澳辦、中聯辦、口交部敢講「光復香港，時代革命」都睇怕唔敢講「攬炒中共 功德無量」掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb9a726068eb7c6285cf8212a79055cd51d30371","tid":1479103,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:31:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"0fc66dfffe95b17a3bbb21b16c19b102ab2131cf","tid":1479103,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"容港治己"},{"pid":"879b861c6406bdbd1b2f00984b8f3c8f417c542c","tid":1479103,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"其實818後 好可能連普選都無用 再升級"},{"pid":"036ee81edf04d9ecbc2f83e8584ace0ac21678b3","tid":1479103,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:37:10.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係叫林奠下台<br />\n當然我都憎到佢入骨<br />\n我哋要嘅係真普選<br />\n如果唔係只會係繼續689 777 898"},{"pid":"42aa5b6d81ed95b6715ea2fcc7a6761cf0f836d5","tid":1479103,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"879b861c6406bdbd1b2f00984b8f3c8f417c542c","tid":1479103,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"其實818後 好可能連普選都無用 再升級"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:37:28.000Z","msg":"攬炒係唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff6f68024e1f183fd2f141b00488ad1ff22ef902","tid":1479103,"uid":248404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實真普選口號好重要。<br />\n<br />\n因為中共而家係將成件事包裝為「港獨」「廢青」。<br />\n其實我地5大訴求裡面已經有我要真普選依條。但牆內既新聞又點會播？<br />\n<br />\n如果我地將口號改為真普選，係大大巴打落中共道。<br />\n因為國內人唔係傻的，佢地會諗點解你地要獨立，又要真普選？咁你地係要普選定獨立？諗多幾諗就會知道中共昆緊佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以依個係真核彈。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"512599a437205e90459a6b00c9a68347809b1e91","tid":1479103,"uid":274907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40954738a3b1df647583f9b6334bf462d8c2b9c0","tid":1479103,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:41:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 2點 維園見<br />\n大家一定要出！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a14Krun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa14Krun.jpg&h=f12c1c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkxLVot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkxLVot.jpg&h=9b3f8527&s={SIZE}\" /><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xg1EfoE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXg1EfoE.jpg&h=24a18478&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vynXB0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vynXB0.jpg&h=613c2f83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSvYvW0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSvYvW0.jpg&h=a8c38726&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRJLaW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRJLaW1.jpg&h=c891df23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/21hv6vm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F21hv6vm.jpg&h=509a7f67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opuuCB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopuuCB2.jpg&h=449e38f4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></div>"},{"pid":"5a4fb5a4bbe65b82efb409de17c530c58e20b929","tid":1479103,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535d6b42e6b91695a7e07c7698b34e89d1d99621","tid":1479103,"uid":132287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ff6f68024e1f183fd2f141b00488ad1ff22ef902","tid":1479103,"uid":248404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實真普選口號好重要。<br />\n<br />\n因為中共而家係將成件事包裝為「港獨」「廢青」。<br />\n其實我地5大訴求裡面已經有我要真普選依條。但牆內既新聞又點會播？<br />\n<br />\n如果我地將口號改為真普選，係大大巴打落中共道。<br />\n因為國內人唔係傻的，佢地會諗點解你地要獨立，又要真普選？咁你地係要普選定獨立？諗多幾諗就會知道中共昆緊佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以依個係真核彈。<br />\n</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:49:44.000Z","msg":"我同你講大陸d人係傻架<br />\n之前周柏豪叫人登記選民都比心話港獨<br />\n同埋就算叫到香港陸沉左 <br />\n中共唔會比大陸人知我地換左口號 <br />\n只會一直spin我地去港獨<br />\n<br />\n不過我好贊成要換口號<br />\n因為個口號唔係比大陸聽 係比外國聽<br />\n依加其實香港既問題已經變左做國際問題<br />\n而普選 自由 民主呢d普世價值最吸外國人支持<br />\n另外最緊要就係當我地有真普選 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求都可以全部解決哂</span></span><br />\n連最難果樣釋放義士都可以由特首特赦或者減刑（公民抗命）<br />\n所以真普選先係我地最主要最主要既一樣野"},{"pid":"144157011d03ac3083216ba652bdb8eef675c3cb","tid":1479103,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0341809b1c75f00a7e6b923cc19b44c2641bed0e","tid":1479103,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99240f62a61569d474e15bd6c9479ed2d1f969f","tid":1479103,"uid":191762,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:50:31.000Z","msg":"其實呢個口號已經有啲柒味"},{"pid":"abb179a42febca72c6667b6707423e6562ca54c5","tid":1479103,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:50:32.000Z","msg":"唔小心負評咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住<br />\n幫推多幾次"},{"pid":"9fa4cc5c4b7381e8f15ff57a02273d4ea369684c","tid":1479103,"uid":271669,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"支持口號：我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0275d88d7c1dd2643b31ada9820459d05fb17056","tid":1479103,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:52:35.000Z","msg":"幾十萬深圳新香港人選舉一定來支持！<br />\n當年已經有人講香港人梗係住深圳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真普選？你自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n小心選呀！dq又係用你（同我）嘅錢再選架炸！"},{"pid":"b97ac81f89fb4d6d6c99309a2d587f8406f1223c","tid":1479103,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fa4cc5c4b7381e8f15ff57a02273d4ea369684c","tid":1479103,"uid":271669,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"支持口號：我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:54:59.000Z","msg":"其實已經有<br />\n<br />\n你地亂咁來選游b<br />\n搞多次真普選<br />\n選到民建聯鄭穎舜<br />\n<br />\n宜家咪幾好<br />\n<br />\n（記得交返你&ldquo;內地&ldquo;另一半資料加快來港）"},{"pid":"7da8485f8c4f91c4e235824bc0fc2fff9f54d421","tid":1479103,"uid":111934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:00:55.000Z","msg":"無主權先係一切問題嘅根源<br />\n中共底下嘅所謂普選, 自己諗<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主講嘅我都支持嘅<br />\n因為爭取港獨會嚇親好多人<br />\n同埋又覺得真普選易入口啲<br />\n起碼好過嗌「香港人加油」嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n如果真係爭到普選, 都唔係壞事<br />\n起碼有機會比香港人知道中共治下無真正民主<br />\n到時再一齊抗爭"},{"pid":"0d07facdb4ed6ec71e9e35239c448982f91b201a","tid":1479103,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:03:06.000Z","msg":"我要真普選"},{"pid":"c05142041a641daf738e1cb25db377f842f583cb","tid":1479103,"uid":212336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:03:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我搭錯時光機返14年?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5ca1336009bd6ee353ba013d5bfa3378bcba8c","tid":1479103,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0275d88d7c1dd2643b31ada9820459d05fb17056","tid":1479103,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:52:35.000Z","msg":"幾十萬深圳新香港人選舉一定來支持！<br />\n當年已經有人講香港人梗係住深圳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真普選？你自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n小心選呀！dq又係用你（同我）嘅錢再選架炸！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"真係俾先算啦，點都嗌咗先<br />\n<br />\n冇普選係問題根源，一定要打住呢個旗號"},{"pid":"52dc5bd52464f669a04bf91777b1520ed92c89a7","tid":1479103,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:07:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港！"}]}